  "body": "### Description\nWith PoS the estimated hight of peers does not get updated as much, which can lead to the situation where we have selected a pivot block, and then disconnect a number of peers until we find a peer that can confirm the pivot block. \nThe solution is to ignore the estimated height of the peers when we are doing PoS and just try peers to confirm the block.\n\n",
